thread.title: Mary

author: Mary
title: Mary
text: I was very pleased with my purchase! The flowering peach tree that I ordered is a very healthy looking and nice sized tree for the price. Order process and delivery was fast and easy. The tree came very professionally boxed and protected with clear instructions and good root protection. I have no complaints and plan to order more plants from you in the future.:)
